Common MFA Factors:
âœ” Something You Know â†’ Password, PIN
âœ” Something You Have â†’ OTP, Phone, Smart Card
âœ” Something You Are â†’ Fingerprint, Face ID

ğŸ’¡ Why Use MFA?
ğŸ”’ Increases security
ğŸš« Prevents unauthorized access
ğŸ“± Used in banking, emails, and social media
